'''Azawax''' d aqejjun yettidiren di tama n tefriqt ugafa, yekkad y isem Azawax seg awal Azewwax (Tamaziɣt): win yettzuxun acku ṣenf agi n iqejjan d win iḥemlen ad isken iman-is. yettidir deg unẓul n tefriqt ugafa, ɣur itargiyen di tama n Mali, Nijer, Burkina faṣu ..., ssawalen-as deɣen Sellugi Atargi.

==Amezruy==
Yella di temnaṭ n Saḥel "anẓul tefriqt ugafa" si zik, ibaned di Tuṛuft deg segwasen n 1970. Asegwas 1981, amqun agraɣlan n teɣri n iqejjan (FCI) tga azal i y Iri Azawax.
Di tdra, Aqejjun agi yella yettwaxdem iw gmer, arured ines iwulem iw ḍfer n waniren d yefrax. Cvaḥa ines teǧǧat daɣen ad yili d aywal n tamunt.
Isem "Azawax" yekkad seg tmaziɣt "azuwax" yellan di teqbaylit.

==Asekkil==

Fsus yarna d amegraw, d aywal izemren ad y aazel iman-is, abaada ɣef ibaṛṛaniyen. ur yettqellib ara ɣef usilef. D addfut yarna d apelfaf, ilaq-as usaɣad aṣebri

